OL,7,FChildren with special educational
OL,8,Fneeds are having to travel long
OL,9,Fdistances to school due to a lack of
OL,10,Fsuitable provision near home, councils
OL,11,Fhave suggested.
OL,13,FBudgets for home to school transport
OL,14,Fare under "considerable pressure" as
OL,15,Fmany special schools are full, which
OL,16,Fis forcing pupils to travel further,
OL,17,Faccording to a Local Government
OL,18,FAssociation (LGA) report.
