OL,7,FSpending by councils on transporting
OL,8,Fchildren and young people with special
OL,9,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,10,F(Send) to schools is predicted to
OL,11,Freach around #1.97 billion in 2025/26,
OL,12,Fup from around #1.73 billion in 2023/
OL,13,F24 and approximately #645 million in
OL,14,F2015/16.
OL,16,FChildren under eight are entitled to
OL,17,Ffree home to school transport if the
OL,18,Fnearest suitable school is more than
OL,19,Ftwo miles away, or more than three
OL,20,Fmiles for older children.
