OL,7,FThe report warned that continuing to
OL,8,Ffulfil the current statutory
OL,9,Fresponsibilities for home to school
OL,10,Ftransport is becoming "increasingly
OL,11,Ffinancially unsustainable" for local
OL,12,Fauthorities.
OL,14,FThe findings have been published
OL,15,Fduring the LGA's three-day annual
OL,16,Fconference in Liverpool this week.
OL,18,FSchools minister Catherine McKinnell
OL,19,Fis due to address council leaders on
OL,20,Fthe Send system at the LGA's
OL,21,Fconference on Wednesday morning.
