OL,7,FDepartment for Education (DfE) data
OL,8,Flast week showed that the number of
OL,9,Feducation, health and care plans
OL,10,F(EHCPs) ` which set out the support a
OL,11,Fyoung person requires for their Send
OL,12,Fneeds ` has increased.
OL,14,FIn total, there were 638,745 EHCPs in
OL,15,Fplace in January, up 10.8% on the same
OL,16,Fpoint last year.
