OL,7,FThe LGA report said the rise in the
OL,8,Fnumber of children and young people
OL,9,Fwho require education in a special
OL,10,Fsetting has "placed considerable
OL,11,Fpressure on home to school transport
OL,12,Fbudgets as most special schools are
OL,13,Ffull, forcing children to travel
OL,14,Ffurther distances to access a place
OL,15,Fthat meets their needs".
OL,17,FCouncils have reported a 40% rise over
OL,18,Fthe last five years in children and
OL,19,Fyoung people with Send (aged under 16)
OL,20,Fneeding home to school transport, the
OL,21,Fresearch suggested.
