OL,7,FArooj Shah, who chairs the LGA's
OL,8,Fchildren and young people board, said:
OL,9,F"The rapidly rising need for home to
OL,10,Fschool transport from children and
OL,11,Fyoung people in Send is yet another
OL,12,Freminder of the huge pressures on the
OL,13,FSend system.
OL,15,F"It is also wrong that children are
OL,16,Fincreasingly having to travel long
OL,17,Fdistances to get to school because of
OL,18,Fa lack of provision near to their home.
OL,20,F"This has to change.
