OL,7,F"We urge the Government in its White
OL,8,FPaper to deliver the comprehensive
OL,9,Freforms the Send system needs, so that
OL,10,Fit is more inclusive and improves
OL,11,Feducational attainment for children.
OL,13,F"This should also include putting
OL,14,Fcouncils on a stable financial footing
OL,15,Fby writing off councils' high needs
OL,16,Fdeficits, which are projected to reach
OL,17,F#5 billion next year."
